3
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:29,500
(Matsuyama)

4
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:34,630
Who are you?

5
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,870
Matsuyama.

6
00:01:45,270 --> 00:01:47,360
Matsuyama, I'm here to kill you.

7
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:55,400
Matsuyama, get out right now!

8
00:01:56,270 --> 00:01:57,630
Welcome. Welcome.

9
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:13,670
Mr. Feng, you're a rare visitor here.

10
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:16,110
I don't understand

11
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:19,160
why you're so hostile to me.

12
00:02:19,910 --> 00:02:22,240
Like you, I like peace too.

13
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,670
I don't want to see blood shed
and war happening.

14
00:02:24,910 --> 00:02:25,960
Shut your mouth.

15
00:02:26,270 --> 00:02:27,030
Feng Guanyu.

16
00:02:28,110 --> 00:02:29,880
Mr. Matsuyama treats you with courtesy.

17
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,600
How dare you be so rude?

18
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,520
Apologize to Mr. Matsuyama now.

19
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,320
Lu Jinzhong,

20
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,470
since you're willing to be the Japanese's lackey,

21
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,880
I'll grant your wish today.

22
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,030
Protect Mr. Matsuyama.

23
00:03:37,550 --> 00:03:38,800
- Take him away.
- Yes.

24
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,190
I'll fight it out with you.

25
00:03:55,390 --> 00:03:55,800
Go.

26
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:01,500
(Matsuyama)

27
00:04:54,070 --> 00:04:56,070
(Oh no, there are so many of them.)

28
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:58,070
(I can't break in anyway.)

29
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,350
(Li Taotao hasn't come yet.)

30
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:24,440
(Oh right, Li Yaoming once mentioned)

31
00:05:25,110 --> 00:05:26,550
(a pipe linked with the rooftop.)

32
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:47,200
How are you feeling, Mr. Feng?

33
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,350
Still not yielding, huh?

34
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,640
Everything of the Feng family,

35
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,000
just like this place,

36
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:07,320
I decide on whether it exists or not.

37
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,000
If I want it destroyed,

38
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:12,270
it'll be destroyed.

39
