40
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:32,830
Your papa, Anti-traitor Corps.

41
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:36,270
Why are you here? Leave!

42
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,510
Huang Weijie.

43
