Mr. Huang,

49
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,670
I admire your courage.

50
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:12,230
But isn't it too boring

51
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:17,760
if I just release Feng Guanyu like this?

52
