What do you mean?

53
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,640
Leave me alone. Run!

54
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,040
Stop it.

55
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,880
Believe it or not, I'll kill you now.

56
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,040
Mr. Huang.

57
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,790
I'll give you a chance to save Feng Guanyu.

58
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,790
What do you want?

59
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:38,590
I want to play a game with you.

60
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,520
I'll count to three.

61
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,520
Let's shoot together.

62
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,440
I'll be shot to death.

63
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,880
Feng Guanyu will die too.

64
00:08:47,910 --> 00:08:48,710
Let's see

65
